WEBVTT

00:00.983 --> 00:02.983
This is
"The Final Word with Perd."

00:03.606 --> 00:06.041
With your host,
Perderick L. Hapley.

00:06.358 --> 00:09.727
Issue number one is the first
issue we're going to talk about.

00:09.795 --> 00:12.630
Is Bobby Newport's campaign
for city council in trouble?

00:13.198 --> 00:14.699
When I say your names,
I want you to respond.

00:15.566 --> 00:16.100
Dylan.

00:16.168 --> 00:18.903
Well, Newport's poll numbers
have been plummeting.

00:18.971 --> 00:21.305
They just fired
his campaign manager,

00:21.372 --> 00:22.672
and where's Bobby?

00:22.740 --> 00:23.841
He's on vacation in Spain.

00:23.908 --> 00:26.276
He's not on vacation,
he's in hiding.

00:26.344 --> 00:28.879
Every time the guy speaks,
he puts his foot in his mouth.

00:28.947 --> 00:30.848
[Laughs]
That's a hilarious image.

00:30.915 --> 00:32.716
A foot in a mouth.

00:32.783 --> 00:35.352
It's a common expression.

00:35.419 --> 00:36.553
Okay.

00:36.620 --> 00:38.154
According to the newest polls,

00:38.222 --> 00:40.422
Leslie knope
is now in second place.

00:40.490 --> 00:42.124
She's just 15 points back.

00:42.192 --> 00:43.392
Whoa, yeah!
[Cheering]

00:43.460 --> 00:44.660
How did she close the gap?

00:44.728 --> 00:45.995
You have to give
a lot of credit

00:46.063 --> 00:47.563
to her campaign manager,
Ben Wyatt.

00:47.630 --> 00:50.399
So apparently, Newport just
fired his campaign manager

00:50.467 --> 00:52.401
because Ben was kicking his ass.

00:52.469 --> 00:55.603
Ben is the best campaign manager
anyone could ever have.

00:55.671 --> 00:57.973
Every move he's made has worked.

00:58.040 --> 01:02.410
He's like a brilliant,
sexy, little hummingbird.

01:02.478 --> 01:03.544
What did you just say?

01:03.612 --> 01:05.180
Nothing.
Keep up the good work.

01:05.248 --> 01:07.415
You're doing great.

01:07.483 --> 01:09.016
[Chuckles]

